<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmación de Compra de Pasaje</title>
    <style>
        /* Email client compatibility resets */
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 35px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 15px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 35px 30px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #059669;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ecfdf5;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .info-table {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }
        .info-table th {
            width: 35%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: left;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .info-table td {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1f2937;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .info-table tr:last-child th,
        .info-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .passenger-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.01);
        }
        .passenger-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #e5e7eb;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .passenger-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .attention-box {
            background-color: #fffbeb;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #78350f;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .attention-box strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        .attention-box p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .badge-seat {
            background-color: #ecfdf5;
            color: #047857;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
            border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
            display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>¡Tu pasaje está confirmado!</h1>
        <p>Hola <strong>{{ buyer_name }}</strong>, gracias por elegir viajar con nosotros.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563; text-align: center;">
            Hemos registrado tu pago de forma exitosa. A continuación dispones del resumen de tu viaje.
        </p>

        <div class="section-title">Detalles del Viaje</div>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Origen</th>
                <td>{{ trip.origin }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Destino</th>
                <td>{{ trip.destination }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Fecha y Hora</th>
                <td>{{ trip.departure_date|date('d/m/Y') }} a las {{ trip.departure_time|date('H:i') }} hs</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Empresa</th>
                <td>{{ trip.company }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Servicio</th>
                <td>{{ trip.service_type }}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="section-title">Detalle de Pasajeros y Asientos</div>
        {% for t in ticket %}
            <div class="passenger-card">
                <table style="width: 100%;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 70%; vertical-align: middle;">
                            <div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 2px;">Pasajero</div>
                            <div style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937;">{{ t.seat_passenger }}</div>
                            <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;">DNI: {{ t.seat_dni }}</div>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 30%; text-align: right; vertical-align: middle;">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">Asiento</div>
                            <span class="badge-seat">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; fill: currentColor; margin-right: 4px; margin-top: -2px;">
                                    <rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="3.5" rx="1" />
                                    <path d="M7,6.5 C7,6 7.5,5.5 8,5.5 h8 c0.5,0 1,0.5 1,1 v8.5 H7 V6.5 Z" />
                                    <rect x="5" y="15.5" width="14" height="5.5" rx="2" />
                                </svg>
                                {{ t.seat_number }}
                            </span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <div class="section-title">Detalles del Pago</div>
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Monto Total del Pasaje</th>
                <td>$ {{ (trip.total_cost|default(object.montoTotal|default(0))/100)|number_format(2, ',', '.') }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Monto Abonado por MP</th>
                <td style="color: #059669; font-weight: 700;">$ {{ payment.amount|number_format(2, ',', '.') }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Método de Pago</th>
                <td>{{ payment.method }}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>ID Transacción</th>
                <td style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563;">{{ payment.transaction_id }}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="attention-box">
            <strong>Requisitos de Embarque:</strong>
            <p>Es obligatorio presentarse 15 minutos antes de la partida y exhibir el DNI/identificación cargado en el boleto al momento de abordar el colectivo. ¡Te deseamos un excelente viaje!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p style="font-weight: 700; color: #4b5563; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 10px;">El Santiagueño Bus</p>
        <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} El Santiagueño Bus. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
        <p>Este es un correo automático, por favor no respondas a este mensaje.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>